me.choco.veinminer.api.veinutils

Class VeinBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.choco.veinminer.api.veinutils.VeinBlock

  • public class VeinBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    General information regarding material and byte data. Every material listed in the configuration file will be loaded as a VeinBlock for easy accessibility in the VeinMiner API

    NOTE: This is subject to change by Minecraft 1.13 where byte data values are no longer suitable to represent block states
